data.title: Northern Section baseball announces all-league, MVP and Coach of the Year Awards
data.meta_description: The baseball season in the Northern Section has concluded but honors and recognition for players continue to come in.
data.text:
The baseball season in the Northern Section has concluded, but honors and recognition for players continue to come in. The Record Searchlight has compiled a list of stars earning all-league accolades.

The following list is of those earning all-league nods in their respective conferences. Each league awards postseason honors in its own manner. Some award Most Valuable Player and Coach of the Year awards while some only name players to the all-league team.
